{"title": "Inside the alternative reality of \u2018sovereign citizens\u2019", "tags": "singapore", "timestamp": "2021-08-23", "content": "SINGAPORE - They say governments are illegitimate and laws do not apply to them. Yet, they want access to what countries provide.\nSovereign citizens, also known as \"sovcits\", have had their claims labelled as strange or dangerous. Sovcits recently gained prominence in the media, with many making headlines around the world for refusing to comply with measures to deal with the pandemic."}